ing Institute of Spain|IGME]]|title=Yacimientos de Sn y Li de La Fregeneda (Mina Feli o de Alabancos)}}</ref>\n\n== Bibliography ==\n;References\n{{reflist}}\n;Bibliography\n* {{Cite journal|last=Roda Robles|first=E.|last2=Pesquera P\u00e9rez|first2=A.|last3=Velasco Rold\u00e1n|first3=F|last4=Font\u00e1n|first4=F|year=1999|title=The granitic pegmatites of the Fregeneda area (Salamanca, Spain): characteristics and petrogenesis|journal=Mineralogical Magazine|volume=63|issue=4|pages=535\u2013558|doi=10.1180/002646199548709}}\n* {{Cite journal|url=https://www.fc.up.pt/peg2007/files/roda.pdf|title=The Fregeneda \u2013 Almendra pegmatitic field (Spain & Portugal): mineral assemblages and regional zonation|first=E.|last=Roda|first2=R.|ref=harv|last2=Vieira|first3=R|last3=Lima|first4=A|last4=Pesquera|first5=F|last5=Noronha|first6=F|last6=Font\u00e1n|journal=Granitic Pegmatites: The State of the Art \u2013 International Symposium. 06th \u2013 12th May 2007, Porto, Portugal|year=2007}}\n* {{Cite journal|journal=[[Mineralogical Magazine]]|year=2016|volume=80|issue=1|pages=103\u2013126|title=Geology and mineralogy of Li mineralization in the Central Iberian Zone (Spain and Portugal)|first=E.|last=Roda-Robles|first2=A|last2=Pesquera|first3=P. P.|last3=Gil-Crespo|first4=R.|last4=Vieira||first5=A|last5=Lima|first6=I.|ref=harv|last6=Garate-Olave|first7=T|last7=Martins|first8=J|last8=Torres-Ruiz|doi=10.1180/minmag.2016.080.049|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200429004539/http://www.sociedadgeologica.es/comisiones/memorias_pgg_rim/memoria_pgg_rim_excursion__r4.pdf}}\n* {{Cite journal|title=Chemical variations and significance of phosphates from the Fregeneda-Almendra pegmatite field, Central Iberian Zone (Spain and Portugal)|first=Encarnaci\u00f3n|last=Roda-Robles|first2=Romeu|last2=Vieira|first3=Alfonso|last3=Pesquera|first4=Alexandre|last4=Lima|journal=Mineralogy and Petrology|volume=100|pages=23\u201334|year=2010|ref=harv|issue=1\u20132|doi=10.1007/s00710-010-0117-7}}\n\n[[Category:Geology of the Iberian Peninsula]]\n", "name_user": "PePeEfe", "label": "safe", "comment": "m ch", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fregeneda%E2%80%93Almendra_pegmatitic_field"}
